---

# ğŸš« Why backend is NOT deployed

Zypher writes its runtime state into:

```
.zypher/
```

Deno Deploy has a **readâ€‘only filesystem**, so Zypher throws:

```
Requires write access to /src/.zypher
```

This is expected, not a bug.

Backend is meant to run **locally only**.

